  </div>

  <div class="sidebar-section">전략 개요</div>
  <nav class="sidebar-nav">
    <a class="sidebar-link active" href="#overview">
      <span class="sidebar-link-num">①</span>발표 전략 프레임
    </a>
    <a class="sidebar-link" href="#script">
      <span class="sidebar-link-num">②</span>단계별 스크립트
    </a>
    <a class="sidebar-link" href="#qna">
      <span class="sidebar-link-num">③</span>예상 질문 & 답변
    </a>
    <a class="sidebar-link" href="#psychology">
      <span class="sidebar-link-num">④</span>청중 심리 전략
    </a>
    <a class="sidebar-link" href="#checklist">
      <span class="sidebar-link-num">⑤</span>발표 전 체크리스트
    </a>
